            .row.section-header Research
            .row
                p My team and I conducted literature research of over 70 peer reviewed and Association for Computer Machinery (ACM) research papers on disaster recovery and game mechanisms.
                p(style='font-weight: bold') 
                    a(href="mailto:eangshelley@gmail.com", target="_blank") Email me
