            .row.sub-section-header Existing Competitive Games
                p My team and I conducted competitive analysis on 6 board games to gain an understanding of game mechanics and how existing board games work. We discovered that many existing competitive games relied on a random factor, team-playing games often required strategy, and competitive collaborative games often required negotiation.
